They believed she was angry that her son had been taken into custody.

Michelle was never registered as missing on the Ohio Missing Persons website.

Neither Deborah or Barbara Knight have heard from police as yet, and both are gathering what details they can from 
watching the news.

But Barbara Knight said she hopes her daughter has been correctly identified.

She added that she would be heartbroken to return to Cleveland only to find that Michelle was still among the missing.

